               <code code="42227-9" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="DRUG ABUSE AND DEPENDENCE SECTION"/>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Drug abuse and dependece have not been reported in patients treated with Hydrocortisone acetate suppositories.</paragraph>
               </text>
